pair_num_list = ['80', '90', '100', '120', '140', '160', '180', '200']
file_name_list = []
for i in range(6, 14):
    file_name = 'column3_narrow/d' + str(i) + '.s2p'
    file_name_list.append(file_name)

aco_v = 3781
prop_time = 242 / aco_v * 1e3

file_name_list.extend(['crosstalk1.s2p', 'crosstalk2.s2p'])
print(file_name_list)
for i in range(8):
    file_name = file_name_list[i]
    print(file_name)
    data = rf.Network(file_name)
    data_s11 = data.s11
    data_s22 = data.s22
    data_s12 = data.s12
    data_s21 = data.s21

    pair_num_prefix = pair_num_list[i]
    plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
    plt.subplot(221)
    data_s11.plot_s_db(label=pair_num_prefix+' pairs, S11')
    plt.subplot(222)
    data_s22.plot_s_db(label=pair_num_prefix+' pairs,s22')
    plt.subplot(223)
    data_s12.plot_s_db_time(label=pair_num_prefix+' pairs, s12')
    plt.xlim(-10, 400)
    plt.axvline(x=prop_time, color='r', linestyle='dashed')
    # start_t = 80
    # end_t = 160
    # data_s21_gated = data_s21.time_gate(start=start_t, stop=end_t, t_unit='ns', window='box')
    # data_s21_gated.plot_s_db_time()
    plt.subplot(224)
    data_s21.plot_s_db_time(label=pair_num_prefix+' pairs, s21')
    plt.xlim(-10, 400)
    plt.axvline(x=prop_time, color='r', linestyle='dashed')
    # start_t = 70
    # end_t = 160
    # data_s12_gated = data_s12.time_gate(start=start_t, stop=end_t, t_unit='ns', window='box')
    # data_s12_gated.plot_s_db_time()
